---
title: Scripts
sub: Often with collaborators
---

<p>
  I don't usually introduce myself as a <em>playwright</em>,
  but I've written a lot of things
  for the stage.
</p>

<!-- intro -->

<ul>
  <li webc:for="script of collections.script.toReversed()">
    <a :href="script.url" @text="script.data.title"></a> &ndash;
    <time
      :datetime="dateFormat(script.date, 'iso')"
      @text="dateFormat(script.date, 'year')"
    ></time>
  </li>
</ul>
